    "We use LOOC to calibrate models in the same setup of §4.3.",
    "We report our results for Llama-2 models in Fig. 3 (cyan lines), finding similar trends in other models (App.",
    "Comparing our method to other calibration approaches, we find LOOC surpasses CC and DC by a wide margin in both performance and bias metrics for prompts with k \" 8, 16 demonstrations.",
